<header>
  <div class="top-stripe row">
    <span class="top-stripe-1"></span>
    <span class="top-stripe-2"></span>
    <span class="top-stripe-3"></span>
    <span class="top-stripe-4"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="logo">Fliplingo.</h1>
  </div>
</header>
<!-- /header -->

<section class="interview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fluid-row">
      <h1>Hi <%= @interviewee.twitter_handle.present? ? "@#{@interviewee.twitter_handle}" : 'there' %>,</h1>
    </div>
    <h2>Fliplingo would like to interview you!</h2>
    <p>
      <% if @interviewee.twitter_handle %>
      We’ve noticed that you communicate in different languages on Twitter and we’re interested to see how you manage this.
      <% else %>
      Do you need to communicate in more than one language on Twitter? If so, we’d love to interview you and discuss how you manage this.
      <% end %>
    </p>
    <p>
      Fliplingo is a Berlin-based start-up aiming to ease and enhance the translation of tweets. Too vague? That’s because we don’t want to bias your thoughts on the subject.
    </p>
      <h2>What does it involve?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          The interview takes no more than 25 minutes. <strong>*</strong>
        </li>
        <li>
          If you’re in Berlin, we’d like to meet with you in person at your favorite coffee place, or <a target="_blank" href="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=betahaus+berlin&ll=52.502743,13.412418&spn=0.070952,0.181789&fb=1&hq=betahaus&hnear=0x47a84e373f035901:0x42120465b5e3b70,Berlin,+Germany&cid=0,0,1623497807966887921&t=m&z=13&iwloc=A">Betahaus</a> (our favorite).
        </li>
        <li>
          If you’re not able to meet, you can take an online survey.
        </li>
        <li>
          Don’t worry, we’re not pitching or selling anything, our goal is just to learn from you.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <br /><br />
      <p class="center">
      Thanks,<br />
      The Fliplingo team.<br />
      <span class="note">*Coffee’s on us :)</span>
      </p>
    </p>
    <div class="help-us">
      <%= form_for @interviewee, html: { class: 'control-group huge' } do |f| %>
          <%= f.email_field :email, class: "span4 email", placeholder: 'Your email address' %>
          <%= f.hidden_field :twitter_handle %>
          <%= f.submit 'HELP US', class: "btn btn-primary btn-huge btn-danger" %>
      <% end %>
      <p class="thanks center">
        Thank you! We'll be in touch.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /.how-it-works -->

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="mailto:matt@fliplingo.com">email</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/fliplingo" target="_blank">twitter</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</footer>
<!-- /footer -->
